gurmukhi: n loBM n coBM ABUqM AByKM ]
transliteration: Na Lobhan Na Chobhan Abhootan Na Abhekhan||
translation: He is without greed, without jealousy, without body and without guise.

gurmukhi: n sqRM n imqRM n nyhM n gyhM
transliteration: Na Satran Na Mitran Na Nehan Na Gehan||
translation: He is without enemy, without friend, without love and without home.
He always has love for all at all times. 9.99.

gurmukhi: n kwmM n kRoDM n loBM n mohM ]
transliteration: Na Kaamannd Na Krodhan, Na Lobhan Na Mohan||
translation: He is without lust, without anger, without greed and without attachment.
He is Unborn, Invincible, the Primal, Non-dual and Imperceptible.

gurmukhi: n jnmM n mrnM n brnM n ibAwDM ]
transliteration: Na Janamannd Na Maranan, Na Barananng Na Biaadhan||
translation: He is without birth, without death, without colour and without ailment.

gurmukhi: n rogM n sogM ABY inribKwpM ]10]100]
transliteration: Na Rogadg Na Sogadg Abhai Nirbikhaadhan||10||100||
translation: He is without malady, without sorrow, without Fear and without hatred.10.100.
He Invincible, Indiscriminate, Actionless and Timeles.
He is Indivisible, Indefamable, Mighty and Patronless.

gurmukhi: n qwqM n mwqM n jwqM n kwXM ]
transliteration: Na Taatan Na Maatan, Na Jaatan Na Kaayan||
translation: He is without father, without mother, without birth and without body.

gurmukhi: n nyhM n gyhM n BrmM n BwXM ]11]101]
transliteration: Na Nehan Na Gehan, Na Bharamannd Na Bhaayan||11||101||
translation: He is without love, without home, without illusion and without affection. 11.101.

gurmukhi: n rUpM n BUpM n kwXM n krmM ]
transliteration: Na Roopan Na Bhoopan, Na Kaayan Na Karamannd||
translation: He is without form, without hunger, without body and without action.

gurmukhi: n qRwsM n pRwsM n BydM n BrmM ]
transliteration: Na Traasan Na Praasan, Na Bhedan Na Bharamannd||
translation: He is without suffering, without strife, without discrimination and without illusion.
He is Eternal, He is the Perfect and Oldest Entity.
